## Next Steps for You
1. **GitHub Pages Activation**:
   - Go to your repository settings on GitHub: **[PoseFlow Settings > Pages](https://github.com/maheshwari-aniruddh/PoseFlow/settings/pages)**.
   - Under **Build and deployment > Branch**, select **`gh-pages`** and the folder **`/(root)`**.
   - Click **Save**.
2. **Local Development**:
   - To use the AI features on the live site, simply run [./start_yoga_web.sh](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/Yogabuddy-backup-original/start_yoga_web.sh) on your local machine. The site will automatically connect to your local backend.

